ut offers, events and updates from The Independent.\", \"from\": 344, \"to\": 564, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 344, \"end\": 354, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Adam Peaty\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Olympic Games\", \"from\": 374, \"to\": 396}, {\"ngram\": \"his career\", \"from\": 424, \"to\": 434}, {\"ngram\": \"bookmarks\", \"from\": 471, \"to\": 480}, {\"ngram\": \"offers\", \"from\": 514, \"to\": 520}, {\"ngram\": \"events\", \"from\": 522, \"to\": 528}, {\"ngram\": \"updates\", \"from\": 533, \"to\": 540}, {\"ngram\": \"The Independent\", \"from\": 546, \"to\": 561}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy notice \\\"I am just a normal person that's good at my job, really,\\\"Adam Peatytells me.\", \"from\": 565, \"to\": 666, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ourPrivacy notice\", \"from\": 570, \"to\": 587}, {\"ngram\": \"just a normal person\", \"from\": 594, \"to\": 614}, {\"ngram\": \"my job\", \"from\": 630, \"to\": 636}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's hard to argue with the second part: the 29-year-old transformed the world ofswimming, holding two world records and enjoying an eight-year unbeaten run in the 100m breaststroke.\", \"from\": 667, \"to\": 849, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the second part\", \"from\": 691, \"to\": 706}, {\"ngram\": \"the world ofswimming\", \"from\": 736, \"to\": 756}, {\"ngram\": \"two world records\", \"from\": 766, \"to\": 783}, {\"ngram\": \"an eight-year unbeaten run\", \"from\": 797, \"to\": 823}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But this invincible streak came to an end in 2022 when a rushed return from a fractured foot saw theCastoreathlete take fourth at theCommonwealth Games.\", \"from\": 851, \"to\": 1003, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this invincible streak\", \"from\": 855, \"to\": 877}, {\"ngram\": \"an end\", \"from\": 886, \"to\": 892}, {\"ngram\": \"a rushed return\", \"from\": 906, \"to\": 921}, {\"ngram\": \"a fractured foot\", \"from\": 927, \"to\": 943}, {\"ngram\": \"theCastoreathlete\", \"from\": 948, \"to\": 965}, {\"ngram\": \"theCommonwealth Games\", \"from\": 981, \"to\": 1002}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That same year, Peaty split from his partner, Eirianedd Munro, and he has since spoken candidly about his experiences withdepression.\", \"from\": 1004, \"to\": 1137, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1060, \"end\": 1065, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Munro\", \"score\": 0.9999999975734681, \"rank\": 2.396992060370702e-09, \"text\": \"Munro\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Munro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Munro\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Peaty\", \"from\": 1020, \"to\": 1025}, {\"ngram\": \"his partner\", \"from\": 1037, \"to\": 1048}, {\"ngram\": \"his experiences withdepression\", \"from\": 1106, \"to\": 1136}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For these reasons and more, preparing for the2024 Paris Olympic Gameswas one of the hardest challenges he's ever faced, and in March 2023 he reached a point where swimming had \\\"broken\\\" him.\", \"from\": 1139, \"to\": 1328, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1189, \"end\": 1194, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.0620119729879845e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these reasons\", \"from\": 1143, \"to\": 1156}, {\"ngram\": \"the2024\", \"from\": 1181, \"to\": 1188}, {\"ngram\": \"the hardest challenges\", \"from\": 1219, \"to\": 1241}, {\"ngram\": \"March\", \"from\": 1266, \"to\": 1271}, {\"ngram\": \"a point\", \"from\": 1288, \"to\": 1295}, {\"ngram\": \"swimming\", \"from\": 1302, \"to\": 1310}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was then that he wrote a contract with himself, brokering an internal deal to dedicate the next 14 months to \\\"hardcore training\\\".\", \"from\": 1330, \"to\": 1462, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a contract\", \"from\": 1356, \"to\": 1366}, {\"ngram\": \"an internal deal\", \"from\": 1391, \"to\": 1407}, {\"ngram\": \"the next 14 months\", \"from\": 1420, \"to\": 1438}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"hardcore training\", \"from\": 1442, \"to\": 1460}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The goal?\", \"from\": 1463, \"to\": 1472, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The goal\", \"from\": 1463, \"to\": 1471}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To be happy at the Olympic Games, and to come away with a result he could be proud of.\", \"from\": 1473, \"to\": 1559, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 1488, \"to\": 1505}, {\"ngram\": \"a result\", \"from\": 1529, \"to\": 1537}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Here, he reveals more about theworkouts, swimming sessions and mindset shift that got him there.\", \"from\": 1560, \"to\": 1656, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"theworkouts\", \"from\": 1588, \"to\": 1599}, {\"ngram\": \"swimming sessions\", \"from\": 1601, \"to\": 1618}, {\"ngram\": \"mindset shift\", \"from\": 1623, \"to\": 1636}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a contract with himself, at a point when he was \\\"almost broken\\\", that got Peaty to Paris.\", \"from\": 1658, \"to\": 1754, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1748, \"end\": 1753, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.0620119729879845e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a contract\", \"from\": 1665, \"to\": 1675}, {\"ngram\": \"a point\", \"from\": 1693, \"to\": 1700}, {\"ngram\": \"Peaty\", \"from\": 1739, \"to\": 1744}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This contract revolved around three questions: \\\"What are you trying to achieve, do you know the price of that, and are you willing to pay that cost?\\\"\", \"from\": 1755, \"to\": 1904, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This contract\", \"from\": 1755, \"to\": 1768}, {\"ngram\": \"around three questions\", \"from\": 1778, \"to\": 1800}, {\"ngram\": \"the price\", \"from\": 1847, \"to\": 1856}, {\"ngram\": \"that cost\", \"from\": 1893, \"to\": 1902}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"What was I trying to achieve - was it a medal, or to be happy at the Olympic games?\", \"from\": 1906, \"to\": 1990, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 1945, \"to\": 1952}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic games\", \"from\": 1972, \"to\": 1989}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a mixture of both,\\\" he tells me.\", \"from\": 1991, \"to\": 2030, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a mixture\", \"from\": 1998, \"to\": 2007}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was going to take dedication and 14 months of hardcore training, as well as exposing myself to losses, being a different athlete and playing the long game.\\\"\", \"from\": 2031, \"to\": 2191, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"dedication\", \"from\": 2053, \"to\": 2063}, {\"ngram\": \"14 months\", \"from\": 2068, \"to\": 2077}, {\"ngram\": \"hardcore training\", \"from\": 2081, \"to\": 2098}, {\"ngram\": \"losses\", \"from\": 2130, \"to\": 2136}, {\"ngram\": \"a different athlete\", \"from\": 2144, \"to\": 2163}, {\"ngram\": \"the long game\", \"from\": 2176, \"to\": 2189}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But the answer [to the final question] was yes, I was willing to do that.\", \"from\": 2193, \"to\": 2267, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the answer\", \"from\": 2198, \"to\": 2208}, {\"ngram\": \"the final question\", \"from\": 2213, \"to\": 2231}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As soon as I asked myself those three questions, and I knew the answers to them, it was a non-negotiable for me.\", \"from\": 2268, \"to\": 2380, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those three questions\", \"from\": 2294, \"to\": 2315}, {\"ngram\": \"the answers\", \"from\": 2328, \"to\": 2339}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was something that had to happen, because you do not want to regret something that you could've done.\\\"\", \"from\": 2381, \"to\": 2486, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 2388, \"to\": 2397}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 2452, \"to\": 2461}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And he was good to his word, training day after day and securing a spot in the Team GB swimming squad.\", \"from\": 2488, \"to\": 2590, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his word\", \"from\": 2507, \"to\": 2515}, {\"ngram\": \"day\", \"from\": 2536, \"to\": 2539}, {\"ngram\": \"a spot\", \"from\": 2553, \"to\": 2559}, {\"ngram\": \"the Team GB swimming squad\", \"from\": 2563, \"to\": 2589}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But things did not go to plan in Paris, with Peaty missing out on a third consecutive Olympic 100m breaststroke gold by just 0.02 seconds after contracting Covid during his final preparations.\", \"from\": 2591, \"to\": 2783, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2624, \"end\": 2629, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.0620119729879845e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 2595, \"to\": 2601}, {\"ngram\": \"Peaty\", \"from\": 2636, \"to\": 2641}, {\"ngram\": \"a third consecutive Olympic 100m\", \"from\": 2657, \"to\": 2689}, {\"ngram\": \"breaststroke gold\", \"from\": 2690, \"to\": 2707}, {\"ngram\": \"just 0.02 seconds\", \"from\": 2711, \"to\": 2728}, {\"ngram\": \"Covid\", \"from\": 2747, \"to\": 2752}, {\"ngram\": \"his final preparations\", \"from\": 2760, \"to\": 2782}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite this, he says he does not \\\" regret one training session or decision I made\\\".\", \"from\": 2784, \"to\": 2868, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one training session\", \"from\": 2827, \"to\": 2847}, {\"ngram\": \"decision\", \"from\": 2851, \"to\": 2859}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I realised that the pain of regret is always going to be worse than the pain of losing, so I wrote that contract with myself, I did it, and I got a good result,\\\" Peaty tells me, two months on from the event.\", \"from\": 2870, \"to\": 3078, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the pain\", \"from\": 2887, \"to\": 2895}, {\"ngram\": \"regret\", \"from\": 2899, \"to\": 2905}, {\"ngram\": \"the pain\", \"from\": 2939, \"to\": 2947}, {\"ngram\": \"losing\", \"from\": 2951, \"to\": 2957}, {\"ngram\": \"that contract\", \"from\": 2970, \"to\": 2983}, {\"ngram\": \"a good result\", \"from\": 3017, \"to\": 3030}, {\"ngram\": \"Peaty\", \"from\": 3033, \"to\": 3038}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 3068, \"to\": 3077}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You have got to be a warrior.\", \"from\": 3080, \"to\": 3110, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a warrior\", \"from\": 3100, \"to\": 3109}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You have got to fight every single day, not back down and choose ways to work harder and smarter.\", \"from\": 3111, \"to\": 3208, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ways\", \"from\": 3176, \"to\": 3180}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There was no stone unturned in the hard work, the deliverables and the results, and I could not have done anything more.\", \"from\": 3209, \"to\": 3329, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no stone\", \"from\": 3219, \"to\": 3227}, {\"ngram\": \"the hard work\", \"from\": 3240, \"to\": 3253}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 3315, \"to\": 3323}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was unfortunate that we got dealt a bad hand in Paris with illness, and certain calls and strategies that were made which were not beneficial.\", \"from\": 3330, \"to\": 3475, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3381, \"end\": 3386, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.0620119729879845e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a bad hand\", \"from\": 3367, \"to\": 3377}, {\"ngram\": \"illness\", \"from\": 3392, \"to\": 3399}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But at the same time they still happened, so it is what it is.\\\"\", \"from\": 3476, \"to\": 3539, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the same time\", \"from\": 3483, \"to\": 3496}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's never just a case of 'This result defines me',\\\" he adds.\", \"from\": 3541, \"to\": 3603, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"just a case\", \"from\": 3553, \"to\": 3564}, {\"ngram\": \"This result\", \"from\": 3569, \"to\": 3580}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His training helped him unlock an even greater work ethic and resilience, and through this he's been left \\\"happy with the person I am, and the skills I have acquired\\\".\", \"from\": 3604, \"to\": 3771, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His training\", \"from\": 3604, \"to\": 3616}, {\"ngram\": \"an even greater work\", \"from\": 3635, \"to\": 3655}, {\"ngram\": \"the person\", \"from\": 3722, \"to\": 3732}, {\"ngram\": \"the skills\", \"from\": 3743, \"to\": 3753}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read more:I tried Alex Yee's running workout and it humbled me in just 40 minutes Peaty's training regime has changed throughout his career.\", \"from\": 3773, \"to\": 3914, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3791, \"end\": 3799, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Yee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Alex Yee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Yee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Yee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"just 40 minutes\", \"from\": 3839, \"to\": 3854}, {\"ngram\": \"Peaty's training regime\", \"from\": 3855, \"to\": 3878}, {\"ngram\": \"his career\", \"from\": 3902, \"to\": 3912}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As a teen, all the way up to the age of 24, he would do five gym workouts and 10 swimming sessions per week, covering roughly 55,000m in the pool.\", \"from\": 3915, \"to\": 4061, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a teen\", \"from\": 3918, \"to\": 3924}, {\"ngram\": \"the age\", \"from\": 3944, \"to\": 3951}, {\"ngram\": \"five gym workouts\", \"from\": 3971, \"to\": 3988}, {\"ngram\": \"10 swimming sessions\", \"from\": 3993, \"to\": 4013}, {\"ngram\": \"week\", \"from\": 4018, \"to\": 4022}, {\"ngram\": \"roughly 55,000m\", \"from\": 4033, \"to\": 4048}, {\"ngram\": \"the pool\", \"from\": 4052, \"to\": 4060}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Some of those days, especially when I was in school and college, were 4am or 5am starts,\\\" he says.\", \"from\": 4063, \"to\": 4162, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those days\", \"from\": 4072, \"to\": 4082}, {\"ngram\": \"school\", \"from\": 4109, \"to\": 4115}, {\"ngram\": \"college\", \"from\": 4120, \"to\": 4127}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And they'd be 8pm finishes, with school in the day.\", \"from\": 4163, \"to\": 4215, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"8pm finishes\", \"from\": 4178, \"to\": 4190}, {\"ngram\": \"school\", \"from\": 4197, \"to\": 4203}, {\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 4207, \"to\": 4214}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was very, very challenging.\", \"from\": 4216, \"to\": 4246, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"As I have got older, we have had to be a bit more strategic with my time and recovery because it takes a little bit longer for the nervous system.\\\"\", \"from\": 4248, \"to\": 4396, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my time\", \"from\": 4314, \"to\": 4321}, {\"ngram\": \"recovery\", \"from\": 4326, \"to\": 4334}, {\"ngram\": \"the nervous system\", \"from\": 4376, \"to\": 4394}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Peaty also has more commitments now than he did at the start of his career, which was another reason for streamlining his plans.\", \"from\": 4398, \"to\": 4526, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Peaty\", \"from\": 4398, \"to\": 4403}, {\"ngram\": \"more commitments\", \"from\": 4413, \"to\": 4429}, {\"ngram\": \"the start\", \"from\": 4449, \"to\": 4458}, {\"ngram\": \"his career\", \"from\": 4462, \"to\": 4472}, {\"ngram\": \"another reason\", \"from\": 4484, \"to\": 4498}, {\"ngram\": \"his plans\", \"from\": 4516, \"to\": 4525}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You have to prioritise - the training comes first,\\\" he explains.\", \"from\": 4528, \"to\": 4593, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the training\", \"from\": 4554, \"to\": 4566}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Then the recovery comes second, and everything else has to [fall back in the] pecking order, which is a format I wasn't really happy with when I had George [Peaty's four-year-old son].\", \"from\": 4594, \"to\": 4779, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the recovery\", \"from\": 4600, \"to\": 4612}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 4631, \"to\": 4641}, {\"ngram\": \"the] pecking order\", \"from\": 4668, \"to\": 4686}, {\"ngram\": \"a format\", \"from\": 4697, \"to\": 4705}, {\"ngram\": \"George [Peaty's four-year-old son\", \"from\": 4744, \"to\": 4777}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That had to change a little bit because you want to put his needs first, but you also want to be a performance athlete.\\\"\", \"from\": 4780, \"to\": 4900, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a little bit\", \"from\": 4799, \"to\": 4811}, {\"ngram\": \"his needs\", \"from\": 4836, \"to\": 4845}, {\"ngram\": \"a performance athlete\", \"from\": 4877, \"to\": 4898}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the run-up to the Paris Olympics, Peaty's revised weekly schedule usually comprised three or four trips to the gym and eight or nine pool sessions - a cocktail of longer aerobic swims, sprints, hard intervals intended to boost his VO2 max and recovery sessions.\", \"from\": 4902, \"to\": 5166, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5136, \"end\": 5143, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/VO2_max\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"VO2 max\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/VO2_max\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/VO2_max\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the run-up\", \"from\": 4905, \"to\": 4915}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 4919, \"to\": 4937}, {\"ngram\": \"Peaty's revised weekly schedule\", \"from\": 4939, \"to\": 4970}, {\"ngram\": \"three or four trips\", \"from\": 4989, \"to\": 5008}, {\"ngram\": \"the gym\", \"from\": 5012, \"to\": 5019}, {\"ngram\": \"pool sessions\", \"from\": 5038, \"to\": 5051}, {\"ngram\": \"a cocktail\", \"from\": 5054, \"to\": 5064}, {\"ngram\": \"longer aerobic swims\", \"from\": 5068, \"to\": 5088}, {\"ngram\": \"sprints\", \"from\": 5090, \"to\": 5097}, {\"ngram\": \"hard intervals\", \"from\": 5099, \"to\": 5113}, {\"ngram\": \"recovery sessions\", \"from\": 5148, \"to\": 5165}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Everything was always calculated and it could change depending on where my body was at,\\\" Peaty says.\", \"from\": 5168, \"to\": 5269, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Everything\", \"from\": 5169, \"to\": 5179}, {\"ngram\": \"my body\", \"from\": 5241, \"to\": 5248}, {\"ngram\": \"Peaty\", \"from\": 5258, \"to\": 5263}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Around that you also have responsibilities like being a father, business partners, commercial work and ambassadorships, so it never really stops.\\\"\", \"from\": 5270, \"to\": 5417, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"responsibilities\", \"from\": 5297, \"to\": 5313}, {\"ngram\": \"a father\", \"from\": 5325, \"to\": 5333}, {\"ngram\": \"business partners\", \"from\": 5335, \"to\": 5352}, {\"ngram\": \"commercial work\", \"from\": 5354, \"to\": 5369}, {\"ngram\": \"ambassadorships\", \"from\": 5374, \"to\": 5389}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His schedule, in the gym and in the pool, also changes throughout the year to reflect where he is with his training.\", \"from\": 5419, \"to\": 5535, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His schedule\", \"from\": 5419, \"to\": 5431}, {\"ngram\": \"the gym\", \"from\": 5436, \"to\": 5443}, {\"ngram\": \"the pool\", \"from\": 5451, \"to\": 5459}, {\"ngram\": \"the year\", \"from\": 5485, \"to\": 5493}, {\"ngram\": \"his training\", \"from\": 5522, \"to\": 5534}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He and his team are constantly tinkering, with the final few months before a major competition being \\\"all about maintenance and finding that extra one per cent in your performance\\\" - an approach he likens to tuning up anF1car.\", \"from\": 5536, \"to\": 5762, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his team\", \"from\": 5543, \"to\": 5551}, {\"ngram\": \"the final few months\", \"from\": 5583, \"to\": 5603}, {\"ngram\": \"a major competition\", \"from\": 5611, \"to\": 5630}, {\"ngram\": \"maintenance\", \"from\": 5648, \"to\": 5659}, {\"ngram\": \"that extra one per cent\", \"from\": 5672, \"to\": 5695}, {\"ngram\": \"your performance\", \"from\": 5699, \"to\": 5715}, {\"ngram\": \"an approach\", \"from\": 5719, \"to\": 5730}, {\"ngram\": \"anF1car\", \"from\": 5754, \"to\": 5761}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When you may start off, you may not be getting the performance you want - a bit likeMcLarenthis season,\\\" says Peaty.\", \"from\": 5764, \"to\": 5881, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the performance\", \"from\": 5812, \"to\": 5827}, {\"ngram\": \"Peaty\", \"from\": 5875, \"to\": 5880}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But eventually you get halfway through the season, or towards the end, and you start to shape that car into something that's very specific and very fast.\", \"from\": 5882, \"to\": 6036, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the season\", \"from\": 5922, \"to\": 5932}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 5945, \"to\": 5952}, {\"ngram\": \"that car\", \"from\": 5977, \"to\": 5985}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 5991, \"to\": 6000}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You are looking at every single little detail, whether that's on the cameras, on the data we are given on recovery, or finding new ways to train.\", \"from\": 6038, \"to\": 6184, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"every single little detail\", \"from\": 6058, \"to\": 6084}, {\"ngram\": \"the cameras\", \"from\": 6104, \"to\": 6115}, {\"ngram\": \"the data\", \"from\": 6120, \"to\": 6128}, {\"ngram\": \"recovery\", \"from\": 6145, \"to\": 6153}, {\"ngram\": \"new ways\", \"from\": 6166, \"to\": 6174}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's continually shifting and we are constantly learning as athletes and coaches how to to find a formula that works.\\\"\", \"from\": 6185, \"to\": 6303, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 6245, \"to\": 6253}, {\"ngram\": \"coaches\", \"from\": 6258, \"to\": 6265}, {\"ngram\": \"a formula\", \"from\": 6281, \"to\": 6290}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read more:Stanley Tucci got into the 'best shape of his life' at 63 with this training method Peaty boasts biceps like bowling balls, but his pre-Olympicgymtrips were not geared towards looking good - every workout was programmed with the sole intention of improving his performance.\", \"from\": 6305, \"to\": 6589, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6315, \"end\": 6328, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stanley_Tucci\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stanley Tucci\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stanley_Tucci\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stanley_Tucci\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 'best shape\", \"from\": 6338, \"to\": 6353}, {\"ngram\": \"his life\", \"from\": 6357, \"to\": 6365}, {\"ngram\": \"this training method\", \"from\": 6378, \"to\": 6398}, {\"ngram\": \"Peaty\", \"from\": 6399, \"to\": 6404}, {\"ngram\": \"biceps\", \"from\": 6412, \"to\": 6418}, {\"ngram\": \"bowling balls\", \"from\": 6424, \"to\": 6437}, {\"ngram\": \"his pre\", \"from\": 6443, \"to\": 6450}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympicgymtrips\", \"from\": 6451, \"to\": 6466}, {\"ngram\": \"every workout\", \"from\": 6506, \"to\": 6519}, {\"ngram\": \"the sole intention\", \"from\": 6540, \"to\": 6558}, {\"ngram\": \"his performance\", \"from\": 6572, \"to\": 6587}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We want to build strength and power in the muscles, and convert that into going faster in the pool,\\\" he says.\", \"from\": 6591, \"to\": 6701, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"strength\", \"from\": 6609, \"to\": 6617}, {\"ngram\": \"power\", \"from\": 6622, \"to\": 6627}, {\"ngram\": \"the muscles\", \"from\": 6631, \"to\": 6642}, {\"ngram\": \"the pool\", \"from\": 6682, \"to\": 6690}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is no point in me going into the gym and doing stuff aimlessly.\\\"\", \"from\": 6702, \"to\": 6773, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no point\", \"from\": 6712, \"to\": 6720}, {\"ngram\": \"the gym\", \"from\": 6738, \"to\": 6745}, {\"ngram\": \"stuff\", \"from\": 6756, \"to\": 6761}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In more recent years, his gym sessions have prioritised compound exercises like thesquat,bench pressand pull-up.\", \"from\": 6775, \"to\": 6887, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more recent years\", \"from\": 6778, \"to\": 6795}, {\"ngram\": \"his gym sessions\", \"from\": 6797, \"to\": 6813}, {\"ngram\": \"compound exercises\", \"from\": 6831, \"to\": 6849}, {\"ngram\": \"thesquat\", \"from\": 6855, \"to\": 6863}, {\"ngram\": \"bench pressand pull-up\", \"from\": 6864, \"to\": 6886}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These involve recruiting multiple muscles at the same time, usually to move heavy loads, making them a top option for Peaty's training goals.\", \"from\": 6888, \"to\": 7029, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"multiple muscles\", \"from\": 6913, \"to\": 6929}, {\"ngram\": \"the same time\", \"from\": 6933, \"to\": 6946}, {\"ngram\": \"heavy loads\", \"from\": 6964, \"to\": 6975}, {\"ngram\": \"Peaty's training goals\", \"from\": 7006, \"to\": 7028}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His coaches also employ supersets (two exercises performed back to back with no rest in between) as part of a technique called complex training.\", \"from\": 7031, \"to\": 7175, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His coaches\", \"from\": 7031, \"to\": 7042}, {\"ngram\": \"supersets\", \"from\": 7055, \"to\": 7064}, {\"ngram\": \"two exercises\", \"from\": 7066, \"to\": 7079}, {\"ngram\": \"no rest\", \"from\": 7108, \"to\": 7115}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 7131, \"to\": 7135}, {\"ngram\": \"a technique\", \"from\": 7139, \"to\": 7150}, {\"ngram\": \"complex training\", \"from\": 7158, \"to\": 7174}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You will go for something really heavy, and pair it with something bodyweight and really fast,\\\" Peaty explains.\", \"from\": 7177, \"to\": 7289, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 7194, \"to\": 7203}, {\"ngram\": \"something bodyweight\", \"from\": 7235, \"to\": 7255}, {\"ngram\": \"Peaty\", \"from\": 7274, \"to\": 7279}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So I might do [back] squats paired with countermovement jumps [max height vertical jumps from a standing start].\\\"\", \"from\": 7290, \"to\": 7404, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"back] squats\", \"from\": 7306, \"to\": 7318}, {\"ngram\": \"countermovement jumps\", \"from\": 7331, \"to\": 7352}, {\"ngram\": \"max height vertical\", \"from\": 7354, \"to\": 7373}, {\"ngram\": \"a standing start\", \"from\": 7385, \"to\": 7401}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Exercise (perform the moves below as a superset) Sets and reps Rest Barbell back squat 5 sets of 5 repetitions 0 seconds Countermovement jump 5 sets of 5 repetitions 120 seconds When using this training technique, Peaty also ups the weight he's lifting with each set.\", \"from\": 7406, \"to\": 7682, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the moves\", \"from\": 7424, \"to\": 7433}, {\"ngram\": \"a superset\", \"from\": 7443, \"to\": 7453}, {\"ngram\": \"Sets\", \"from\": 7455, \"to\": 7459}, {\"ngram\": \"Rest Barbell\", \"from\": 7469, \"to\": 7481}, {\"ngram\": \"back squat 5 sets\", \"from\": 7482, \"to\": 7499}, {\"ngram\": \"5 repetitions\", \"from\": 7503, \"to\": 7516}, {\"ngram\": \"0 seconds\", \"from\": 7517, \"to\": 7526}, {\"ngram\": \"Countermovement jump\", \"from\": 7527, \"to\": 7547}, {\"ngram\": \"5 sets\", \"from\": 7548, \"to\": 7554}, {\"ngram\": \"5 repetitions\", \"from\": 7558, \"to\": 7571}, {\"ngram\": \"this training technique\", \"from\": 7595, \"to\": 7618}, {\"ngram\": \"Peaty\", \"from\": 7620, \"to\": 7625}, {\"ngram\": \"the weight\", \"from\": 7635, \"to\": 7645}, {\"ngram\": \"each set\", \"from\": 7664, \"to\": 7672}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If he's doing back squats, he will lift 100kg for the first set then work his way up to five reps at 150kg for the final round - something he likes to do on a Monday morning, when his body is feeling fresh after his regular Sunday rest day.\", \"from\": 7683, \"to\": 7923, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"squats\", \"from\": 7702, \"to\": 7708}, {\"ngram\": \"100kg\", \"from\": 7723, \"to\": 7728}, {\"ngram\": \"the first set\", \"from\": 7733, \"to\": 7746}, {\"ngram\": \"his way\", \"from\": 7757, \"to\": 7764}, {\"ngram\": \"150kg\", \"from\": 7784, \"to\": 7789}, {\"ngram\": \"the final round\", \"from\": 7794, \"to\": 7809}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 7812, \"to\": 7821}, {\"ngram\": \"a Monday morning\", \"from\": 7840, \"to\": 7856}, {\"ngram\": \"his body\", \"from\": 7863, \"to\": 7871}, {\"ngram\": \"his regular Sunday rest day\", \"from\": 7895, \"to\": 7922}]}, {\"senten